            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (8) 日尾盤一度翻黑失守 2 萬 4 千點，但在台達電撐盤、台積電跌幅收斂下，指數最後一盤翻紅上漲 17.49 元，收 24021.26 點，成交量 4206 億元；而本周在電子權值輪番發力下，周漲 586.88 點或 2.5%。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6098621/l/a91d4b533c2f4f4db3374fda8bc735a7.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台股盤後〉翻紅小漲17點險守2萬4大關 電子權值輪動周漲586點。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 今日小跌 5 元收 1175 元、聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 同樣收黑，AI 股方面，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 收平盤、台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 漲 2.25 元，收歷史新高價 637 元、廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 漲 1%。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>高價股方面，信驊 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5274:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5274\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5274-TW</a>) 收黑，但弘塑 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3131:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3131\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3131-TW</a>)、旺矽 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6223:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6223\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6223-TW</a>)、印能科技 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7734:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7734\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7734-TW</a>)、緯穎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6669:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6669\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6669-TW</a>)、健策 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3653:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3653\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3653-TW</a>)、嘉澤 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3533:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3533\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3533-TW</a>) 等均漲 2-3% 以上，奇鋐 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3017:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3017\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3017-TW</a>) 大漲 6%，而智邦 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2345:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2345\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2345-TW</a>) 今日也一度觸及千元大關。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>此外，PCB 族群今日再度點火，金像電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2368:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2368\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2368-TW</a>) 漲停、健鼎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3044:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3044\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3044-TW</a>) 漲 9.5%、臻鼎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4958:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4958\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4958-TW</a>) 漲 4%；其餘強勢電子指標股還有漢唐 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2404:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2404\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2404-TW</a>) 漲 6%、南亞科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2408:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2408\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2408-TW</a>) 漲 4%；傳產指標則以大成鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2027:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2027\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2027-TW</a>) 漲逾 7% 較強。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
